data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Location, Location, Location. Large 3 Bedroom 2.5 Bathroom Two Story Home with a Side Entry Oversize 2 Car Garage on a Fenced Corner Lot. Master Suite on 1st Floor. Open Floor Plan. Kitchen with Island. Giant Living Room with Wood Burning Fireplace and Built-in Cabinets. Massive Florida Room not included in Heated Sq Ft which could easily be added. Parklike Setting in Backyard with a Built-in Jacuzzi. Walk to Bauder Elementary, Seminole Middle and High School. Ready to Close Estate Sale. Sold As Is. Perfect Location and Layout! Home needs TLC so come see what it takes to make it your own.
